1. Unpack openejb-standalone-8.0.11.tar.gz

2. Update OPENEJB_HOME in setenv.sh

3. Compile the beans and client:
   bash make.sh

4. Run the EJB server (in another console window):
   bash run-server.sh

5. Deploy your beans to the running server:
   bash run-deploy.sh

6. Run the client:
   bash run-client.sh

7. Stop the EJB server gracefully
   bash stop-server.sh
